summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 27E, page 86, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Lots 1-5 incl. and portions of Lots 6-7, lying easterly of line 100 ft. east of and parellel to the east margin of 22nd Ave. W., Block 131, Gilman Addition.
